- Tests for construction/validation and lifecycle values:
  - Added [test/jidoka_durable_core_test.exs](/Users/mhostetler/Source/OrigJido/jidoka/test/jidoka_durable_core_test.exs) covering:
    - `new/1` valid construction paths and invalid status/id cases for each durable entity
